{"tid":237982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發夢仲夢到自己趕功課/讀書?","createTime":"2017-05-10T17:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T15:41:49.000Z","uid":105498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e189cafdf70d8caefb0f5563ea222e0a0dd7582","tid":237982,"uid":105498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:47:01.000Z","msg":"小弟已大專畢業近一年<br />\n有時發夢仲會夢到番學時期啲19野(冇記錯全部都係中學生活)，趕功課，考試前一日爆seed溫書，多數係呢兩樣<br />\n雖然係發緊夢，但發到呢類夢既時候，個腦真係好似好用力咁運作緊，幾真實&mdash;&mdash;不斷用腦做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不斷溫書將文字記入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(具體內容唔知係咩，但個腦係好用力記住啲空白野，只能咁樣形容佢地，唔係1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n夢左一段長時間之後，自己先會意識到係發緊夢，好自然咁同自己講「你已經番完學 唔駛再理呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n就係咁，間唔中又loop一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己喺呢啲夢入面真係好大壓力好真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明已經畢哂業，仲會繼續發呢啲on9夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都係咁"},{"pid":"bc3c938812ef602005d8faadf81c8f562c27a9dd","tid":237982,"uid":29138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"有 幾享受 好多時都係夢中得到啟發<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀建築學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbd692933670a5991150cf8d4647a7a080ab6b5","tid":237982,"uid":105498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 幾享受 好多時都係夢中得到啟發<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀建築學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時真係會夢到啲好特別既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔即刻mark低好易會唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdd5df7fbdfdc002437b2fd9827aba985943ad5","tid":237982,"uid":105498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl